metadata.name: Tourists
metadata.description:
Let me take you for a walk around my city. We will visit some of the most iconic places, as well as go down ordinary streets. Stop at the cafés and look through the windows. And it will rain. Let’s breath in this atmosphere, let’s take it all in.
